{"tid":164773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英：公務員班子穩定沒有離職潮","createTime":"2017-03-21T01:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T04:45:06.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f503dbfd9bd6a8d66e85f7df6c02e5ea08bdb19","tid":164773,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:59:54.000Z","msg":"行政長官梁振英，出席行政會議前表示，對於民主300+選委，傾向在特首選舉中支持曾俊華，他不感到意外。梁振英指，香港就好像西方有民主選舉的地方，支持者提名和投票給候選人都清清楚楚，並非新鮮或稀奇的事，所以民主派選委不投票給林鄭月娥，而投票支持曾俊華，沒有甚麼人會感到意外。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英又澄清，政府整個班子包括公務員班子都十分穩定，並無離職潮，指有關報道只是選舉炒作，無事實根據。梁振英又否認會留任特區政府的任何決策職位，或出任內地港澳工作協調小組成員，指沒有這樣的消息和計劃，並不真確，純屬揣測。"},{"pid":"9575dd0ed8b057f8749daa8201529e832ed11aa5","tid":164773,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:00:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=929989&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D929989%26csid%3D261_341&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=adcf6c7f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=929989&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"074325e39374d1b907476e502055a4fda344ead0","tid":164773,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:10:03.000Z","msg":"我唔會參選特首 召喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22c6af4a6141978220ab8bd521cff9ce0e80569","tid":164773,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4d384f349d55e706d8adadc50e135ab4e438fa","tid":164773,"uid":7534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:32:10.000Z","msg":"班子 ... 真係屌老母垃圾蝗語"},{"pid":"976e134d12c735a556c474fb578ef74250ce3b54","tid":164773,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:04:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班子 ... 真係屌老母垃圾蝗語</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我會叫團隊或者我Ｄ０靚"},{"pid":"561302655c346916105e9dc892d37eb38d1be3ce","tid":164773,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:08:41.000Z","msg":"同我公司否認有離職潮一樣嘅喂。"},{"pid":"d13d4acc1fc8588e859c5f904a4014e5698a65ff","tid":164773,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:30:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ba952b2d72897a044beaadbeca5bef4b689db2","tid":164773,"uid":2707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:45:06.000Z","msg":"中共班子"}]}